    "body": "It seems like I encountered a similar issue on one of the nodes I restarted this morning. It was due to a huge RocksDB compaction that took around 15 minutes, which is not normal. Compaction are usually very fast. \r\n \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229522250-9b93388c-9500-4857-b4ea-dabc9e4ea3bf.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229522301-802ac9fb-8347-443b-948f-cf0306b6d900.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229522612-c7a3fbd3-c90d-4f60-b921-5f5e5f0837f1.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229522697-567dc887-72d5-49e9-95e3-9dc0e9959110.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229522769-b0d8b9d8-ca57-4012-b0e3-6cb1c2eb1824.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229522936-70265c28-d1ba-4e5e-8589-92daf7e1c390.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5099602/229523050-3f75fbe3-c378-4b11-b5a9-29f01c0b7756.png)\r\n",
