    "body": "I've just remembered that we [recently downgraded RocksDB](https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/6930) in Teku due to a user reporting long (multi-minute) freezes. RocksDB is not our default, but some users prefer it. The reported symptoms from our user look very similar to those in this issue.\r\n\r\nMore info [here](https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/6930). Also cross-reference [here](https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/issues/6940).",
